willing to meet them in the middle.

44:07.562 --> 44:11.522
Oh. Is that where you
want to live your life?

44:11.732 --> 44:12.813
In the middle?

44:14.193 --> 44:16.810
- Called compromise.
- No, it's called sacrifice.

44:17.029 --> 44:19.021
Giving up who you are
to be someone you're not.

44:19.240 --> 44:21.323
Sometimes that's what it takes.

44:21.534 --> 44:24.151
