46:16.107 --> 46:17.894
Come on, Nate. You can do this.

46:20.194 --> 46:21.810
Start over.

46:40.381 --> 46:41.872
And your wedding picture.

46:48.806 --> 46:50.923
And your honeymoon picture.

47:03.487 --> 47:06.104
