48:57.184 --> 49:00.302
- Who am I?
- You're going to choose an alter ego and role play.

49:00.521 --> 49:03.810
Trust me, this works. I used it
whenever my brides were really nervous

49:04.024 --> 49:07.813
about their wedding. It breaks you out of
that shell and gives you that confidence

49:08.737 --> 49:11.070
