I am from Normandy.

50:23.729 --> 50:25.436
Normandy?

50:25.648 --> 50:27.810
Oui, yes.

50:28.025 --> 50:30.517
Have you... this painting here?

50:32.446 --> 50:34.438
[woman] No, I haven't.

50:34.657 --> 50:36.899
You see on the surface

50:37.117 --> 50:40.861
Adam and Eve in a disrupted
Eden, is a familiar topic.

50:41.080 --> 50:44.369
But if you Io <i>o</i> k at it,
